// About
"about_title" = "PicBase64 v%@";
"about_text" = "A lightweight and efficient macOS menu bar tool that makes converting between images and Base64 a breeze.\n\nFeatures\n✂️  Capture and convert to Base64 in one click — no more online converters\n🔄  Bi-directional: Image → Base64 / Base64 → Preview Image\n🎨  Multiple output formats: data URL / Markdown / JSON / Plain text\n🧩  Drag & drop base64 text or images to preview\n⌨️  Global hotkeys for quick capture and copy\n⚡️  Pure Swift + native AppKit implementation, zero dependencies\n📦  Tiny installer size, minimal memory footprint\n\nKeyboard Shortcuts\n⌥1 Capture Region  ⌥2 Capture Window  ⌥3 Full Screen\n⌥C Clipboard Image to Base64\n⌥V Read Base64 to Preview\n⌘, Open Settings\n\nCredits\nIcons by Lucide open source project\nLicensed under MIT License\n\n© 2025 PicBase64 Contributors";

